      • equals

        public boolean equals(Object o)
        Compares the specified object with this ScoreElement for equality.

        This implementation first checks if the specified object is a ScoreElement. If not, it returns false; if so, it checks if the specified object is this ScoreElement. If not, it returns false; if so, it compares the duration value of both the score elements.

        Overrides:
        equals in class Object
        Parameters:
        o - object to be compared for equality with this ScoreElement.
        Returns:
        true if the specified object is equals to this ScoreElement; false otherwise.
